{"title":"人生礼赞——献给优秀共产党员陈金水","authors":["嵇亦工"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":7,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生礼赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给优秀共产党员陈金水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嵇亦工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，远远地我望着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就站在那里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同一杆鲜亮的战旗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶湛湛蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踩茫茫雪域……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，久久地我注视你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就站在那里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹似一支不泯的火炬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃亮了亘古寒夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融化着千年冰迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那猿不攀登的世界屋脊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你开创着崭新世界；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那鹰不落脚的生命禁区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你繁衍着生命气息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那风暴与严寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终日笼罩的雪川冰崖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用信念与忠贞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢书写生命的意义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此，藏北高原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你迈开第一串步履；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此，安多雪城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你扎下第一顶帐篷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也扎下了一个个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心愿与期冀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里缺少的是绿色与氧气；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不缺的却是斗争的勇气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里冰冷的是飞飘的雪粒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火热的则是工作的乐趣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海拔四千八百米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对于常人简直不可思议"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对于你恰恰是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"施展才华的广阔天地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，四千八百米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是——一个劳动者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无愧无悔的人生高度；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是——一个共产党人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有始有终的精神境地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，二十二载月圆月缺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天下——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一朵七彩云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是你用汗水编织？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，三十三回寒来暑去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原上——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一束格桑花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是你用智慧染碧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十度热血青春呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧区内——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一座毡房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都洋溢过你的欢歌笑语；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十三年艰苦征程呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰雪中——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一行足印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都烙刻着你的忠贞不渝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就站在那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用双手垒筑起地球上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一高度的气象站；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以母亲的名义——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向祖国亲切汇报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的创造力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就站在那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用生命填写下气象学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一页空白的历史；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以东方的声音——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向世界庄严宣告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的奇迹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安多城头的百叶箱呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是你博大的胸臆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日讲述着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是云情、是雨况，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你绵绵的情愫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双湖怀中的测风仪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是你明澈的双目"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时时告示着的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是气流、是风力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你暖暖的爱意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在那里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每日每夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜马拉雅山的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从你掌心升起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雅鲁藏布江的星月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自你肩头滑去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在那里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝朝暮暮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羌塘草原的鹰隼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你脚下游弋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青藏公路的霓虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你胸前缠系。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，真正的人子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生来就应这般气派；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，真正的男儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活着就该这样站立！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远地我望着你呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久久地我注视你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你站在共和国的版图上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厚实的身躯，丰碑般矗立；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你站在亿万人的心灵中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚挺的脊梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如一杆大笔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用全部青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你整整一生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋力书写一个字："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左一撇——唐古拉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右一捺——横断山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两座巍峨而挺拔的山脉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成一个巨大的“人”字！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个人呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是你……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}